pageContext.claim: “No matter what information is given to the crazed Democrats from the No Collusion Mueller Report, it will never be good enough. Behind closed doors the Dems are laughing!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats say the Trump White House has not complied with any document requests. Special counsel Robert Mueller decided not to bring charges on illegal coordination or conspiracy, but he documented numerous contacts between Trump campaign members and Russian individuals. Mueller also declined to reach a decision on whether Trump obstructed justice. But the special counsel documented a sustained effort by Trump to derail the investigation, oust Mueller, and possibly influence witness testimony. Mueller did not bring charges but his report casts Trump in a damning light.
